posting_body: ['MUST HAVE STRONG CREDIT!', 'NO EVICTIONS!', 'NO CRIMINAL RECORDS!', 'NO EXCEPTIONS!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!', 'CALL NOW!!!!!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!!', 'Email Me, Call Me, or Text!!!!', 'Shawn Kaminsky', 'show contact info', 'Comfy, with character galore, this enormous 3 bedroom 2.5 bath condo is the perfect home away from home.', 'Spit floorpan, tile floors, newer stainless appliances, granite counters, wood shutters, huge soaking tub & glass shower, tons of storage, full-size washer & dryer in laundry room, & massive wraparound balcony that offers great views & privacy in the treetops.', 'This home is thoughtfully stocked with everything you need for a long or short term stay.', "The Metropolitan is a luxury, mid-rise, boutique residence, located right in Downtown's creatively reimagined The Square (formerly CityPlace), Downtown's home to trendy new shops, restaurants & entertainment.", 'Metropolitan boasts 24 hr doorman, rooftop pool, hot tub & outdoor lounge, fitness center, clubroom & so much more']
